{"tid":2394176,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"“上游”風險已經成為中資券商的最大風險","createTime":"2021-02-04T04:02:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T17:33:56.000Z","uid":81028,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7f5efdc53c72a258b0dfdc198c5ab2ba65690e0a","tid":2394176,"uid":81028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:02:46.000Z","msg":"大香港大部分中資券商經歷過GME 被所謂&ldquo;<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">上游</span></span></strong>&rdquo;服務供應商停止買賣股票後。已經有部分散戶尋求更為安全的買賣平台。<br />\n<br />\n簡單解析個風險，買賣股票的流程：<br />\n1. 中資券商 --》上游服務供應商 --》交易所<br />\n2. 銀行/部分券商 --》交易所<br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong>銀行</strong></strong>是其中一個很好的選擇，如果你係長線投資者，不是每月不停出出入入。<br />\n以蘋果公司為例，20年的回報股票來計算大約37倍，係銀行買左，之前就唔洗理，過一段日子等收錢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.moneyhero.com.hk/zh/securities-account/us-stock-account\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneyhero.com.hk%2Fzh%2Fsecurities-account%2Fus-stock-account&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRA4SWcZegttS7JwdJctbizM%3D&h=c58976cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.moneyhero.com.hk/zh/securities-account/us-stock-account</a><br />\n<br />\n參考：<br />\n<strong>[Urgent] 今日收市前一定要List  曬可以買GME 的券商。買唔到的全部blacklist。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/gBMopS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/gBMopS</a></strong>"},{"pid":"d371876bac4194b776cc8248de30d5f3ec54334d","tid":2394176,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"長線月供呢？ 俾銀行食手續費風險仲大"},{"pid":"91cb17285ebc7d317779a0af0c15eaadf13ce37c","tid":2394176,"uid":81028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:06:43.000Z","msg":"Quote 之前個post 所講，銀行貴就係貴在唔會係重要時刻禁止你買賣股票。"},{"pid":"ffbd5e6fe0a5c35e3906c5d2ff75675287e5000a","tid":2394176,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:07:04.000Z","msg":"點解佢地唔可以直接買賣？富途咁美國自己都有公司點解都要經ib?"},{"pid":"8812a65de907c47686e6a1d3077ebb4e2755afda","tid":2394176,"uid":33338,"like"